# cogentia.js runtime queue — typed continuations created by `cogentia.js continuation`.
# These are working-session state (task definitions, dormant chains, predecessors).
# The persistent audit trail lives in .cogentia/audit.jsonl, which IS tracked.
# Continuations are intentionally ephemeral; the audit log is the source of truth.
.cogentia/continuations/
.cogentia/cache/
.cogentia/index/
